    <h1>Bitter Gourd</h1>
    <img src="https://media.istockphoto.com/id/177537480/photo/gold-wheat-field-and-blue-sky.jpg?s=612x612&w=0&k=20&c=CAxLzTeCt4qBn7fifuoOh70ycoHr9w7FyeNVzkde_IM=" alt="">
